ygData.messageBody:
Finally swept my EQ directory of screenshots.

http://www.mindspring.com/~rhoneyman/everquest

blackplate*.jpg Finally, all black, now I need a longsword and
shield.

azarack*.jpg All angles of the Azarack Island (full, 8 mobs)
Should help analysis of breaking it for those
who haven't done it yet.

eyeofveeshan1.jpg Found him in PoS, visually it's a bug, I wonder what
it really should be.

fearplane1.jpg This one is funny as hell.

quillmane1.jpg I've killed this damn thing many times and all legs
of course until a ranger KS's then it has a cloak.

vox*.jpg Still shots of Vox, not very impressive, but I was
bored.

cazicthule1.jpg Had a bunch of shots of him, this was the best.

wolves1.jpg Oasis wolf attack.

I had a screenshot of Bildge when I killed him, but I can't find it.
And I forgot to take one of the named rat in DC, Jetsam I think his
name is. Lost the one of the girl with the Crown of Leaves too.

Harmonic, Bildge Hunter.
